graph LR
    TrustyAI[TrustyAI Service Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    TrustyAI -->|container orchestration| Kubernetes[Kubernetes v1.19+]
    TrustyAI -->|metrics scraping| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    TrustyAI -.->|routes & oauth| OpenShift[OpenShift v4.6+]
    TrustyAI -.->|service mesh| Istio[Istio]
    TrustyAI -.->|inference monitoring| KServe[KServe v1beta1]
    TrustyAI -.->|job queue| Kueue[Kueue]
    TrustyAI -.->|data storage| Database[PostgreSQL/MySQL]

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI Dependencies
    TrustyAI -->|patches & monitors| KServeInt[KServe<br/>Internal RHOAI]
    TrustyAI -->|deployment patches| ModelMesh[Model Mesh<br/>Internal RHOAI]
    TrustyAI -.->|service discovery| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>Internal RHOAI]
    TrustyAI -->|traffic routing| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh Istio<br/>Internal RHOAI]

    %% External Services
    TrustyAI -.->|model downloads| HuggingFace[Hugging Face Hub]
    TrustyAI -->|metrics push| Prometheus[Prometheus]

    %% Integration Points
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|uses| TrustyAI
    Dashboard -->|displays| TrustyAI

    %% Dependency categories
    subgraph "Required External"
        Kubernetes
        PrometheusOp
    end

    subgraph "Optional External"
        OpenShift
        Istio
        KServe
